	# Invariant 
		A property that remains unchange when a specified transformation is applied #web
		
	# published
		An object is said to be published when it can be referred by others #39
		
	# escaped
		-> 	An object is said to be escaped when the object is not 
			supposed to be published at that time #40
			
	# Not properly constructed
			-> 	When an object publish itself during consrtuction phase it is said to be
				not propertly constrcuted 